[C++] gcc 9.2.0

#include <iostream>
#include <algorithm>
#include <string>
#include <vector>

using namespace std;
vector<string> split_str_into_str_arr(string s, string delimiter)
{
	size_t pos = 0;
	string token;
	vector<string> vs;
	
	while ((pos = s.find(delimiter)) != string::npos)
	{
		token = s.substr(0, pos);
		cout << token << endl;
		vs.push_back(token);
		s.erase(0, pos + delimiter.length());
	}
	vs.push_back(s);
	
	return vs;
}

int main(void)
{
    auto vs = split_str_into_str_arr("scott>=tiger>=mushroom", ">=");
    for(auto& it : vs)  cout << it << " ";
    
    return 0;
}
